OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782503276
OL,3,CDUP commissions 'independent review'
OL,4,Cover Donaldson
OL,6,FThe DUP have commissioned a
OL,7,F"specialised and detailed" independent
OL,8,Freview over issues arising following
OL,9,Fthe conviction of Jeffrey Donaldson.
OL,11,FIt comes after DUP Minister Paul Givan
OL,12,Ftold UTV he was aware of "rumours"
OL,13,Fabout Donaldson's lifestyle in
OL,14,Frelation to adults but not about
OL,15,Fcrimes involving children.
OL,17,FThere were several reports on Friday
OL,18,Fincluding from the Belfast Telegraph
OL,19,Fand BBC over claims made about the
OL,20,Fformer MP's behaviour.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782503276
OL,3,CDUP commissions 'independent review'
OL,4,Cover Donaldson
OL,6,FThey included reports that he engaged
OL,7,Fin hypocritical behaviour at times,
OL,8,Falthough not criminal behaviour.
OL,10,FAnother claim was that several people
OL,11,Fin the DUP were made aware of an
OL,12,Fallegation made by a young woman, that
OL,13,Fshe had been exploited by Donaldson.
OL,14,FHowever, no formal complaint was made.
OL,16,FOn Monday, a jury of seven men and
OL,17,Ffive women at Newry Crown Court
OL,18,Funanimously found Donaldson, 63,
OL,19,Fguilty of 18 sexual offences,
OL,20,Fincluding one count of rape, against
OL,21,Ftwo women when they were children.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782503276
OL,3,CDUP commissions 'independent review'
OL,4,Cover Donaldson
OL,6,FPaul Givan MLA told UTV: "I think you
OL,7,Fneed to differentiate between what
OL,8,Fwere crimes against children, and what
OL,9,Falso then are rumors.
OL,11,F"There were rumors about Jeffrey
OL,12,FDonaldson, but again, having evidence
OL,13,Fis what's important in that respect.
OL,15,F"And what I'm hearing in terms of the
OL,16,Frumors, these related to adults in
OL,17,Fthat respect, not of a criminal nature.
OL,19,F"But I don't have the information on
OL,20,Fthis. People are asking me and others
OL,21,Fto speculate about unknowns."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782503276
OL,3,CDUP commissions 'independent review'
OL,4,Cover Donaldson
OL,6,FIn a statement the DUP said: "The
OL,7,Fparty has no knowledge of these issues
OL,8,Fraised and is shocked to learn of
OL,9,Fthese alleged incidents highlighted.
OL,11,F"The Democratic Unionist Party has
OL,12,Fwell established processes for dealing
OL,13,Fwith complaints and standards.
OL,15,F"At no time did the party receive any
OL,16,Fcomplaints internally or externally
OL,17,Fabout inappropriate and/or criminal
OL,18,Fbehaviour by Jeffrey Donaldson."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782503276
OL,3,CDUP commissions 'independent review'
OL,4,Cover Donaldson
OL,6,FLater on Friday in another statement,
OL,7,Fthe party said: "The DUP acted swiftly
OL,8,Fwhen former member Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,9,Fwas first charged.
OL,11,F"As a party we believe in the rule of
OL,12,Flaw and that criminal proceedings must
OL,13,Ftake their full course. Justice has
OL,14,Fbeen served with the guilty verdicts
OL,15,Fagainst him.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
