OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782503276
OL,3,CDUP commissions 'independent review'
OL,4,Cover Donaldson
OL,6,F"The Party Leader Gavin Robinson MP,
OL,7,FDeputy Leader Michelle McIlveen MLA
OL,8,Fand Party Chairman are deeply
OL,9,Fconcerned by allegations that have
OL,10,Fsurfaced in recent days relating to
OL,11,Finappropriate behaviour on behalf of
OL,12,FJeffrey Donaldson, and the indication
OL,13,Fthat some may have had knowledge of
OL,14,Finappropriate behaviour but which was
OL,15,Fnever reported to the Party Officers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
